snippet.title: Japanese Money Simulator - I made a game!
snippet.description:
https://wendal.itch.io/japanese-money-simulator play the game here!

I've made a video game about Japanese currency. If you're thinking of travelling to Japan, or like puzzle games, give it a shot.

Was made with the Godot Engine.
